969
00:54:25,429 --> 00:54:29,265
I'll try to call you in the morning.
Would you please show Miss Wade out?

970
00:54:31,018 --> 00:54:33,186
MAN:
The response scenario's in place.

971
00:54:33,562 --> 00:54:36,981
