977
00:54:56,919 --> 00:54:59,003
Nothing, unless we miss.

978
00:54:59,254 --> 00:55:02,215
- Are we gonna miss?
- No, sir.

979
00:55:04,885 --> 00:55:07,720
- How many people work in the building?
- We went through this.

980
00:55:07,888 --> 00:55:10,181
How many people working
in the damn building?

981
00:55:10,474 --> 00:55:13,393
I have the numbers here, Mr. President.
